<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">فِيهِ مَسَائِلُ:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">الأُولَى:</span> تَفْسِيرُ الآيَاتِ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">الثَّانِيَةُ:</span> صِفَةُ الشَّفَاعَةِ المَنْفِيَّةِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">الثَّالِثَةُ:</span> صِفَةُ الشَّفَاعَةِ المُثْبَتَةِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">الرَّابِعَةُ:</span> ذِكْرُ الشَّفَاعَةِ الكُبْرَى وَهِيَ المَقَامُ المَحْمُودُ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">الخَامِسَةُ:</span> صِفَةُ مَا يَفْعَلُهُ <span class="special">ﷺ</span>؛ أَنَّهُ لَا يَبْدَأُ بِالشَّفَاعَةِ، بَلْ يَسْجُدُ؛ فَإِذَا أُذِنَ لَهُ شَفَعَ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">السَّادِسَةُ:</span> مَنْ أَسْعَدُ النَّاسِ بِهَا؟<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">السَّابِعَةُ:</span> أَنَّهَا لَا تَكُونُ لِمَنْ أَشْرَكَ بِاللَّهِ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c5">الثَّامِنَةُ:</span> بَيَانُ حَقِيقَتِهَا.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>